<sect1 id="dir_1155230619ab793a5e69143311c57b80_1autotoc_md575">
<title>helios::engine::modules::ui::layout::components</title><para>Layout-related UI components.</para>
<para>This namespace contains components used by the UI layout system for formatting and presenting data in text widgets.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_1155230619ab793a5e69143311c57b80_1autotoc_md576">
<title>Components</title><para><table rows="3" cols="2"><row>
<entry thead="yes"><para>Component  </para>
</entry><entry thead="yes"><para>Description  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>TimeFormatterComponent</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Formats elapsed or remaining time into a display string via <computeroutput>std::vformat</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>NumberFormatterComponent</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Formats arithmetic values (scores, health, etc.) into a display string via <computeroutput>std::vformat</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry></row>
</table>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_1155230619ab793a5e69143311c57b80_1autotoc_md577">
<title>TimeFormatterComponent</title><para>Holds a format string and a <computeroutput>TimeDisplayMode</computeroutput>. The format string receives two integer arguments (minutes, seconds). When duration is zero, the display mode falls back to <computeroutput>Elapsed</computeroutput>.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_1155230619ab793a5e69143311c57b80_1autotoc_md578">
<title>NumberFormatterComponent</title><para>Holds a <computeroutput>std::vformat</computeroutput>-compatible format string that accepts a single arithmetic argument. Used by binding systems such as <computeroutput>Score2UiTextUpdateSystem</computeroutput> and <computeroutput>MaxScore2UiTextUpdateSystem</computeroutput> to convert numeric game state into text.</para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
